==Japanese==
===Adjective===
'''すっぱい''' (''[[suppai]]'')

* '''[[酸っぱい]]'''
# [[Sour]].

====Etymology====
* Root is '''[[酸い]]''' ([[すい]], ''[[sui]]'') "[[sour]]", from '''[[酢]]''' ([[す]], ''[[su]]'') "[[vinegar]]".
* Related to the word '''[[すし]]''' (''[[sushi]]'') "vinegared [[rice]]".

==== Related terms ====
* '''[[酸い]]''' ([[すい]], ''[[sui]]''): [[Sour]].  Less commonly heard than '''すっぱい'''.

